sections.heading: Repealed.Section 34-15-2 - Repealed.
sections.text:
History:Laws 2003, ch. 94, § 1; repealed by Laws 2008, ch. 7, § 4.

Repealed.— Laws 2008, ch. 7, § 4, repealed 34-15-1 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 2003, ch. 94, § 1, relating to the domestic violence offender treatment fund, effective July 1, 2008. For provisions of former section,seethe 2007 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
